column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.subclass,s.z as redshift,  s.plate, s.mjd, s.fiberid, s.veldisp, p.lnLDeV_g, p.lnLstar_g,p.lnLexp_g,  p.fracdev_g FROM PhotoObjall AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid WHERE   s.class = &&& and s.veldisperr > # and s.veldisp > #*s.veldisperr and   p.petroR5#err_u > # and p.petroR5#_u > #*p.petroR5#err_u and   p.petroR5#err_g > # and p.petroR5#_g > #*p.petroR5#err_g and  p.petroR5#err_r > # and p.petroR5#_r > #*p.petroR5#err_r and  p.petroR5#err_i > # and p.petroR5#_i > #*p.petroR5#err_i and  p.petroR5#err_z > # and p.petroR5#_z > #*p.petroR5#err_z and   p.petroR9#err_u > # and p.petroR9#_u > #*p.petroR9#err_u and   p.petroR9#err_g > # and p.petroR9#_g > #*p.petroR9#err_g and  p.petroR9#err_r > # and p.petroR9#_r > #*p.petroR9#err_r and  p.petroR9#err_i > # and p.petroR9#_i > #*p.petroR9#err_i and  p.petroR9#err_z > # and p.petroR9#_z > #*p.petroR9#err_z and  p.petroR5#_u/P.petroR9#_u < # and   p.petroR5#_g/P.petroR9#_g < # and  p.petroR5#_r/P.petroR9#_r < # and  p.petroR5#_i/P.petroR9#_i < # and  p.petroR5#_z/P.petroR9#_z < # and p.deVAB_u># and p.devab_g>#   and p.devab_r > # and p.devab_i > # and p.devab_z>#
